  <item nodeId="node-1">
    <command xml:space="preserve">SilentCargo</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">Silent Cargo&#x000A;A sci-fi mystery aboard the T-7366D Second Voice by Thomas Evans&#x000A;Release 1 / Serial number 260318 / Inform 7 v10.1.2 / D&#x000A;&#x000A;Airlock&#x000A;The airlock is dimly lit by a thin emergency strip. Several EVA suit lockers stand open along one wall. Most of the suits are gone. The inner hatch leads deeper into the ship.&#x000A;&#x000A;Exits: north.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
