    <command xml:space="preserve">x container</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">A heavy cargo container, bolted to the deck and wired into the ship through thick power conduits. Its surface is marked with a faded Helios Systems Research Division seal.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
