    <command xml:space="preserve">x terminal</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">The terminal flickers to life as you access it. Medical data scrolls across the screen.&#x000A;&#x000A;Available options:&#x000A;- view crew status&#x000A;- view sleep data&#x000A;&gt;</result>
