  <item nodeId="node-70">
    <command xml:space="preserve">s</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">Airlock&#x000A;Bright overhead lights reveal every scrape and dent in the chamber. Several EVA suit lockers stand open along one wall, most of them empty. Deep scratches have been carved into the metal beside the outer hatch: "DON'T LET IT HEAR YOU".&#x000A;&#x000A;Exits: north.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
