    <command xml:space="preserve">w</command>
    <result xml:space="preserve">Crew Quarters&#x000A;Full lighting reveals the cramped quarters in stark detail: unmade bunks, unsecured personal items, and drifting blankets left behind in haste.&#x000A;&#x000A;Exits: east.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
